svt_i2c_system_sequencer Class Reference

Inheritance diagram for class svt_i2c_system_sequencer:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This class is the I2C System sequencer class. This is a virtual sequencer which can be used to control the virtual sequecers of the I2C sub system.
